                    <title>Hi Jeff
Thanks for you reply…</title>
                    <link rel="alternate" href="http://coderetreat.org/xn/detail/6456126:Comment:11045"/>
                                        <id>tag:coderetreat.org,2012-07-23:6456126:Comment:11045</id>
